PASTE THE RESUME HERE (plain text).

Replace this entire file with the full text of your resume — summary,
experience, skills, education, everything. The scout compares each job
description against this text to compute the semantic "resume fit" half of
the match score, so more detail = better matching.

Alternative: drop `resume.pdf` or `resume.docx` into the project root instead;
the scout will read whichever it finds first (pdf/docx need the optional
`pypdf` / `python-docx` packages installed).
